Website: www.pubnub.com

===============================================================================
INTRO
===============================================================================
www.pubnub.com

PubNub + Python + Twisted:

===============================================================================
REQUIRED LIBRARY
===============================================================================
Twisted 10.0.0+
Download Twisted Here: http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/

tar xvfj Twisted-10.0.0.tar.bz2
cd Twisted-10.0.0
sudo python setup.py install

===============================================================================
EXAMPLES
===============================================================================
Open pubnub-example.py for examples.

There are three functions:
    1) Publish     - Push a message.
    2) Subscribe   - Listen for messages.
    3) UnSubscribe - Stop Listening. (optional)


